{% from "components/hero.njk" import hero %}
{% from "components/breadcrumb-trail/macro.njk" import breadcrumbTrail %}

{% extends "layouts/main.njk" %}

{% block content %}
    <main role="main">
        {{ hero(
            titleText = title,
            image = heroImage,
            accent = pageAccent
        ) }}

        <div class="nudge-up">
            <section class="content-box content-box--tinted
                u-inner-wide-only accent--{{ pageAccent }} a--border-top">
                {{ breadcrumbTrail(breadcrumbs, isTinted = true) }}
                <div class="s-prose u-constrained-content-wide">
                    <p>Digital tools and working practices can help civil society organisations to serve people better than ever before. The digital fund makes grants of <strong>£100,000 to £500,000</strong> to help organisations to become more successful.</p>
                    <p><a href="#">Read our post announcing this programme</a></p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="content-box u-inner-wide-only accent--{{ pageAccent }} a--border-top">
                <div class="s-prose u-constrained-content-wide accent-content--{{ pageAccent }}">
                    <h2 id="get-started">Get started</h2>

                    <p>The Digital Fund has multiple strands of funding, each with their own eligibility criteria.</p>
                    <p>Please choose one of the following options so we can provide the right guidance for you.</p>

                    <p><a href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/alternative-funding"
                        class="btn btn--medium accent--pink a--btn">
                        We want help getting started with digital
                    </a></p>
                    <p><a href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/strand-1"
                        class="btn btn--medium accent--blue a--btn">
                        We want to use digital to change our core business
                    </a></p>
                    <p><a href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/strand-2"
                        class="btn btn--medium accent--cyan a--btn">
                        We are already highly digital, and want to scale our impact
                    </a></p>

                    <p>If you would prefer, you can also choose to <a href="#eligibility-details">see all the eligibility criteria</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section
                class="content-box u-inner-wide-only accent--{{ pageAccent }} a--border-top"
                id="eligibility-details">
                <div class="s-prose u-constrained-content-wide accent-content--{{ pageAccent }}">
                    <h2>Full eligibility details</h2>

                    <p>The full eligibility criteria are listed below, we can also provide guidance <a href="#get-started">tailored to your needs</a>.</p>

                    <p>The Digital Funding Programme is currently planning to make awards to just two kind of organisation. These two kinds of organisations must demonstrate they can meet different criteria in order for their application to be successful:</p>

                    <p><strong>Long-established charities with 25 or more staff want to reassess their core activities and fundamental business models, through a digital lens</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Eligibility</li>
                        <li>Success factors</li>
                        <li>Nature of support offered</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><a class="btn btn--small btn--outline"
                        href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/strand-1">Find out more about this funding</a></p>

                    <p><strong>Smaller organisations that have no ‘pre-digital’ legacy structures to modernise, which are poised to deliver impact at real scale</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Eligibility</li>
                        <li>Success factors</li>
                        <li>Nature of support offered</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><a class="btn btn--small btn--outline"
                        href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/strand-2">Find out more about this funding</a></p>

                    <h2>Our policies</h2>

                    <p>It is important to us that you are committed to equalities and the environment. We’ll want to know about your equalities and environmental policies if we are interested in your idea.</p>

                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="https://www.biglotteryfund.org.uk/about-big/our-approach/equalities">Our equality principles</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/environmental-responsibility-for-charities">Visit gov.uk for more information on environmental responsibility</a></li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Get started</h2>

                    <p>If you think this fund might be right for you, choose one of the two options below to get started.</p>

                    <p><a href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/strand-1"
                        class="btn btn--medium accent--blue a--btn">
                        We want to use digital to change our core business
                    </a></p>
                    <p><a href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/strand-2"
                        class="btn btn--medium accent--cyan a--btn">
                        We are already highly digital, and want to scale our impact
                    </a></p>

                    <p><small>The Big Lottery Fund will also soon be commissioning digital experts to offer free assistance to hundreds of voluntary sector organisations looking to build their basic digital skills. The Digital Fund will therefore not be making grants that are focused on basic skills. <a href="/funding/programmes/digital-funding-demo/alternative-funding">You can sign up for updates about free digital assistance here.</a></small></p>

                    <h2>Have any questions?</h2>

                    <p>If you have any questions about eligibility, get in touch with us.</p>
                    <p><strong>Phone</strong>: <a href="tel:03454102030">0345 4 10 20 30</a><strong><br>Text relay</strong>: 18001 plus 0345 4 10 20 30 (for those with a hearing or speech impairment)<strong><br>Email</strong>: <a href="mailto:general.enquiries@biglotteryfund.org.uk">general.enquiries@biglotteryfund.org.uk</a></p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
{% endblock %}
